artifacts.action_items:
[
  {
    "task": "Create a new remote control for a television",
    "owner": "unassigned",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Project Manager: So, this is our project. What we're aiming to do is to create a new remote control for a television."
  },
  {
    "task": "Design the functional components of the remote control",
    "owner": "Industrial Designer",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Project Manager: The method that we're going to use to complete the project, that has three components as such. There's the functional design of the the remote control."
  },
  {
    "task": "Design the conceptual components of the remote control",
    "owner": "Industrial Designer",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Project Manager: but the conceptual design is um perhaps bigger than that and includes the how people are going to use it and and that kind of thing."
  },
  {
    "task": "Design the user interface of the remote control",
    "owner": "User Interface Designer",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "User Interface: um so um in the different um stages of the design, so at first I will be responsible for um for designing the technical functions of the um of the remote control uh then in the in the conceptual design stage I need to um come up with uh interface concept and then in the last um stage I will be responsible for the int infa for the user interface design."
  },
  {
    "task": "Develop a menu-based system or a single button for a menu",
    "owner": "unassigned",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Marketing: You know, so something heading towards that, so it's not overly I mean I don't know what h most of the buttons do on my remote controls, so I figure how many do you need, you know?"
  },
  {
    "task": "Balance innovation with usability to avoid a steep learning curve",
    "owner": "unassigned",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "User Interface: even though it has to be re original we shouldn't uh go like too far away from from the usual ones, because otherwise the new users will just have a lot of problems"
  },
  {
    "task": "Aim for a high battery life",
    "owner": "Industrial Designer",
    "deadline": "none",
    "evidence": "Industrial Designer: Mm . Uh we can aim for I mean we can think about all these little things, but we can aim for something wi that gives a high battery life"
  }
]

